snippet.title: Price for Freedom: Avarice - Prologue
snippet.description:
Price for Freedom: Avarice is based on the webcomic series, It is a top down RPG, heavily inspired by old games such as Baldurs Gate. So expect decent amount of text, and people to talk to. 

Just as the original webcomic the game includes adult material.

Platforms : Windows, Mac, Linux
Developers : Team Dead Deer

to see the uncensored version as well as some exclusive content, Go to our Patreon at https://www.patreon.com/TheAdultGamer

to show your love and support, please subscribe to our channel, hit the bell icon and pledge whatever you can
